## Overview

A full-stack portfolio designed to combine minimal design with dynamic functionality.

It reflects my journey through development, competitive programming, and systems thinking.

## Stack

**Frontend**  
HTML · CSS · JavaScript

**Backend**  
Node.js · Express.js

**APIs & Integrations**  
Codeforces API · GitHub API · Chart.js

## Features

- Responsive cinematic interface
- Real-time Codeforces rating graph
- Dynamic GitHub profile integration
- Smooth transitions and interactions
- Interactive coding profile section
- Structured full-stack architecture

